        <div class="moral">
            <p><strong>üíä THE MORAL OF THE STORY üíä</strong></p>
            <p class="trippy-text">If it sounds too good to be true, it's probably being sold by a sheep in a barn.</p>
            <p><em>Also: The FDA exists for a reason.<br>
            And glitter is not medicine.<br>
            And maybe don't trust health advice from someone who literally grows their product on their own body.</em></p>
